name: CloudCentury
overview:
Cloud Century is consulting and development studio established by NewGround ltd in order to provide services in area of Cloud Computing. Based on about a decade of experience in enterprise Java technologies and software outsourcing we have solid background in software projects development and maintenance. We have more than dozen of successfully accomplished software projects for customers around the world ranging from large scale financial projects to Java application for mobile devices. Our developers are highly skilled professionals with strong experience in Java and system engineering.

Contact us to discuss your needs and to evaluate the cost saving potential for your company.
